Changes in 1.01

  All attribute values and option labels are HTML-escaped.
  
  Explained CGI.pm compatability in POD docs.
  
  Subroutines can now accept hash-refs, thanks to Ron Savage.
  
  Arguments to all functions:
  	Added 'value' as an alias for 'values'.
    Documented that 'defaults' is an alias for 'default'.
  
  Makefile.PL changed to use Module::Build

Changes in 1.00
  
	Initial release.

